snippet.title: Clea - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Mum and Dad have been experimenting on Chaos Servants, but now, the monsters have been let loose. Clea, with her brother in tow, must escape from the Whitlock Mansion.

Watch your back, Clea. Those closest to you may be the real terror.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/981020/Clea/

Clea is a survival horror title with zero cheap jump scares. The game was created as a way for me to express my love for titles such as Resident Evil and Alien Isolation.

Thank you for your support!
